{"tid":1197373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建立勇武組織的財政系統","createTime":"2019-06-10T03:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:26:26.000Z","uid":8244,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acb1fad157ad1ec05a55f9f172422cefa62f117c","tid":1197373,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"傳統和理非 因為金主、議席收入、籌募 令到佢地可以有穩定既財務收入，就算佢地既人失去議席都唔駛餓死<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n但勇武組織無穩定收入來源，成日要擔心手停口停，令到勇武運動好難有可持續性</span><br />\n<br />\n難聽d講如果勇武係有收入，連南亞人都叫得郁去做野<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有迫切性以連登為平台，建立抗爭者既財政系統，咁樣運動先可以長玩長有"},{"pid":"26032fff53eaa50ecb6fa1c84da9549ef3b17877","tid":1197373,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c00844ef1438a7e318651dd9417f03e198a06a1","tid":1197373,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:38:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97401c996a6e5e4448906e561235bf1a4667e955","tid":1197373,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"353e6430b09c4d243e7fcd03ffb39d56432e8073","tid":1197373,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}